Name: Alien Duel Elements
About the game: Challenge your friends on a one-on-one simple, easy-to-handle 2D platform. Play as Aliens mastering elementary powers such as Fire, Frost and Arcanes. Customize your character as well as the Game modes, and let the face-to-face begins! • 2 Local split screen players (NO MODE SOLO) • 4 Different Modes • 3 Playable elements • 20 Levels • Bonuses and other customizations • Includes next update and bug fixing This mini game was created during lockdown and it is in constant development, I hope you will enjoy it. It has been made profitable to allow us to finance our studies and our future projects, thanks in advance to those who will support us.
